  "prompt": "What are the coolest IT companies in Chandigarh, India?",
  "response": "Chandigarh, known for its modern architecture and quality of life, is also home to a growing number of IT companies. Some of the coolest IT companies in Chandigarh include:\n\n1. **Chandigarh Group of Colleges (CGC) IT Services** - They offer various IT services and have a strong emphasis on skill development and innovation.\n\n2. **Tech Mahindra** - Part of the Mahindra Group, this company provides IT services and solutions, specializing in various sectors including telecommunications and enterprise solutions.\n\n3. **K2 Tech** - Emphasizes innovative software solutions and offers services in web development, mobile applications, and digital marketing.\n\n4. **Tricity Web Solutions** - A digital marketing and web development company that focuses on delivering effective online solutions for businesses.\n\n5. **Inovaticus Marketing Solutions** - They specialize in custom software development, digital marketing, and various IT consulting services.\n\n6. **Saffron Tech** - Offers IT solutions focusing on web and mobile application development, software solutions, and digital marketing.\n\n7. **eChai Ventures** - While not strictly an IT company, it focuses on networking and supporting startups, including many in the tech space.\n\n8. **Techno Infonet** - A web and mobile development company that also provides business solutions.\n\n9. **Xpert Digital** - Primarily focused on digital marketing and IT solutions, they work with various clients to enhance their online presence.\n\n10. **Brand Burp** - A creative agency known for its innovative approaches to digital marketing and IT solutions.\n\nThese companies often emphasize innovation, a collaborative work culture, and opportunities for skill development, making them appealing places to work in the IT sector. The tech scene in Chandigarh is evolving, with many startups emerging in addition to established firms, contributing to a vibrant ecosystem.",
